cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.DB, cs.SOC, cs.CL

The paper discusses the challenge of determining dependence between sources of information on the Web, which is a problem related to information retrieval (cs.IR), social networks (cs.SOC), and data management (cs.DB). The proposed solutions also involve natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IR and cs.SI, followed by cs.DB, cs.SOC, and cs.CL.
